Install android studio untuk manfaatkan emulatornya

Tambahkan path:
	$ nano ~/.bashrc
	
	Tambahkan dipaling bawah:
	export ANDROID_HOME=$HOME/Android/Sdk
	export PATH=$PATH:$ANDROID_HOME/tools

Check:
	$ android --version




-=Install flutter=-

Yang dibutuhkan:
	$sudo apt install curl git unzip xz-utils libglu1-mesa

Unduh file:
	https://flutter.dev/docs/get-started/install/linux

Ekstrak:
	$ /apps/ tar xf /Downloads/flutter_linux_1.22.0-stable.tar.xz

Tambahkan path:
	$ nano ~/.bashrc
	
	Tambah dipaling bawah:
	export PATH=$PATH:~/apps/flutter/bin/

Check:
	$ flutter
	$ flutter doctor

Referensi:
	https://www.petanikode.com/flutter-linux/
